- <a href="https://github.com/marcelomatus/gtopt/blob/master/docs/usage.md">Usage Guide</a>
- <a href="https://github.com/marcelomatus/gtopt/blob/master/docs/input-data.md">Input Data Reference</a>
- <a href="https://github.com/marcelomatus/gtopt/blob/master/BUILDING.md">Building Guide</a>

*/
